#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo154_2_Text054"
msgid "That princess was my own daughter...<1.ra>My dear Zelda."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo154_2_Text055"
msgid ""
"And the courageous knight who protected her\n"
"right up to the very end... <1.ra>That knight was none other than you, "
"Link."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo154_2_Text056"
msgid ""
"You fought valiantly when your fate took an\n"
"unfortunate turn.<1.ra>And then, you were taken to the Shrine of\n"
"Resurrection. Here you now stand revitalized, 100\n"
"years later."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo154_2_Text057"
msgid ""
"The words of guidance you have been hearing since\n"
"your awakening are from Princess Zelda herself.<1.ra>Even now, as she "
"works to restrain Ganon from\n"
"within Hyrule Castle, she calls out for your help."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo154_2_Text058"
msgid ""
"However, my daughter's power will\n"
"soon be exhausted. <1.ra>Once that happens, Ganon will freely\n"
"regenerate himself and nothing will stop\n"
"him from consuming our land. "
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo154_2_Text059"
msgid ""
"Considering that I could not save my own kingdom,<1.ra>I have no right to"
" ask this of you, Link... "
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo154_2_Text061"
msgid ""
"Somehow, Ganon has maintained control over all\n"
"four Divine Beasts,<1.ra>as well as those Guardians swarming around\n"
"Hyrule Castle."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo154_2_Text062"
msgid ""
"I believe it would be quite reckless for you to head\n"
"directly to the castle at this point.<1.ra>I suggest...that you make your"
" way east, out to\n"
"one of the villages in the wilderness."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
msgctxt "Demo154_2_Text063"
msgid ""
"Follow the road out to Kakariko Village.<1.ra>There you will find the "
"elder, Impa. <2.ra>She will tell you more about the path that lies ahead."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
msgctxt "Demo154_2_Text064"
msgid ""
"Consult the map on your Sheikah Slate for the\n"
"precise location of Kakariko Village. <1.ra>Make your way past the twin "
"summits\n"
"of the Dueling Peaks.<2.ra>From there, follow the road as it proceeds "
"north..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Demo154_2_Text065"
msgid "But I am powerless here..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo154_2_Text066"
msgid ""
"You must save her...my daughter. <1.ra>And do whatever it takes to "
"annihilate Ganon."
msgstr ""

